headline: FirstCash Holdings (FCFS) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: FirstCash (FCFS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +7.83% and +0.77%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
